# 
# For Dokploy Deployment:
# 1. Set NODE_ENV=production
# 2. Set PORT=5000
# 3. Set SUPABASE_URL and SUPABASE_ANON_KEY from your Supabase project
# 4. Set FRONTEND_URL to your Vercel/deployed frontend URL
# 5. Add your API keys (DEEPSEEK_API_KEY or OPENROUTER_API_KEY)
